name: Diaz Grimm presents: Maui & the Sin (AOTs)

metadata.description:
Each AOT represents partial ownership in Diaz Grimm's new 14 track album 'Māui & the Sin'. What that ownership means will be unveiled along the way. 

Album art will be revealed once sold out or on November 1st when the AOT sales close.

100 AOTs on sale to the public
54 split between featured artists, producers, Video team etc
